quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Ndarahiye kuri iki gisagara c’Imakkat
  90,2,Na wewe uzomanuka muri iki gisagara nyene
  90,3,"Ndarahiye kukintu cavyaye, hamwe nicavutse"
  90,4,Yuko twaremye ikiremwa muntu mungorane nyinshi cane
  90,5,Mbega yiyumvira yuko ata n’umwe yoshobora kumufata
  90,6,"Avuga ati:- narononye amatungo menshi cane"
  90,7,Mbega yiyumvira yuko ata n’umwe amubona
  90,8,Mbega ntitwamuhaye amaso abiri
  90,9,N’ururimi hamwe n’iminwa ibiri
  90,10,Tumwereka inzira zose uko ari zibiri
  90,11,Mbega yarawusatuye uwo musozi
  90,12,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musozi
  90,13,N’uguha umushumvyi uburenganzira bwiwe n’iteka rimukwiye
  90,14,Canke ukamurisha k’umusi w’ikigoyi
  90,15,Impfuvyi y’umugenzi n’iyitari iyumugenzi
  90,16,Canke umukene ataco yifashije
  90,17,"Hanyuma\tabe\tmubemeye\tImana\tyiwe\ty’ukuri,\tnukuburirana ukwihangana nukuburirana mukugiriranira ikigongwe"
  90,18,Abo nibo bantu bo kuruhande rw’amahoro
  90,19,"Mugabo abahakanye amajambo yacu matagatifu, abo nibo bantu bo kuruhande rw’ishari"
  90,20,Umuriro wugarijwe kumpande zose uzoba uri hejuru yabo